@startuml sequence_service_installation_liba4tv_v4
title Service Installation - broadcast (liba4tv)

actor User
box "Android app" #EBF5FF
  participant "Live TV App\n(SetupActivity)" as App
  participant "DtvTvInputService" as TIS
  participant "StreamsXmlReader" as XMLR
  participant "ComediaMiddlewareConnection" as MWC
  participant "ChannelScanner" as CHSC
  participant "ChannelPublisher" as CHPB
end box

box "liba4tv Java API (Android-facing wrapper)" #E8F5E9
  participant "ComediaRouteManagerControl" as ROUTE
  participant "ScanControl" as SCAN
  participant "ScanListener\n(callback na TIS)" as SCANL
  participant "ServiceControl" as SVC
end box

box "Comedia native middleware" #FFF8E1
  participant "Comedia Core (MW)\nInstall logic + Table parser (PAT/PMT/SDT)" as CORE
  database "Service & Mux DB\n(SList + PIDB)" as SDB
  participant "Comedia CHAL (TDAL)\nTDAL_DMD / TDAL_DMX" as CHAL
end box

box "Platform / HAL - demonstration" #FFF3E0
  participant "Tuner SDK / Tuner HAL\n(Cuttlefish: .ts fajl kao izvor)" as TSDK
end box

participant "Android TV Provider\n(TvContract.Channels)" as TVP

User -> App : Initiate scan (first-time install)
App -> TIS : startScan(inputId)

TIS -> XMLR : readScanSourceUrls(context)
XMLR --> TIS : String[] sourceUrls\n(iz res/xml/streams.xml)

TIS -> MWC : getRouteManagerControl() / getScanControl()
MWC --> TIS : ComediaRouteManagerControl, ScanControl
note over MWC : drzi konekciju ka Comedia middleware-u\n(ComediaDtvContext) i Control instance

TIS -> CHSC : startScan(sourceUrls)

CHSC -> ROUTE : getInstallRoute(RouteManagerMediumType.MEDIUM_IP)
ROUTE --> CHSC : routeID
note over ROUTE : MEDIUM_IP = file/URL scan (Cuttlefish)

CHSC -> SCAN : registerListener(scanListener)

== Skeniranje kroz niz izvora (ChannelScanner) ==
loop za svaki sourceUrl u sourceUrls
  CHSC -> SCAN : appendList(append)
  note right of SCAN : append=false samo za prvi izvor (brise staru listu),\nappend=true za sve sledece (akumulira)
  CHSC -> SCAN : autoScan(routeID, sourceUrl)
  SCAN --> CHSC : A4TVStatus
end
note right of SCAN
 poziv prihvacen, skeniranje pokrenuto za prvi izvor;\nostali izvori iz petlje se obradjuju nakon scanFinished (vidi nize)
end note
== Comedia native middleware ==

SCAN -> CORE : pokreni instalaciju na ruti (routeID)
CORE -> CHAL : TDAL_DMD - otvori izvor (file/tuner) na ruti

CHAL -> TSDK : otvori protokol ('file') + otvori section filtere (PAT/PMT/SDT)
TSDK --> CHAL : izvor zakljucan (locked) + sekcije dostupne

CHAL --> CORE : TDAL_DMX - section data (PAT, PMT, SDT)

SCAN --> SCANL : tunerLocked(routeId, true)
SCANL --> CHSC : tunerLocked(routeId, true)

loop za svaki servis/multipleks pronadjen u TS-u
  group Comedia Middleware Core
    CORE -> CORE : parsiraj PAT (PID 0)\n-> potrebno: lista (ONID, TSID) + PMT_PID po servisu
    CORE -> CORE : parsiraj PMT (po servisu, na PMT_PID)\n-> potrebno: SID, video/audio/subtitle PID-ovi, PCR PID, stream type
    CORE -> CORE : parsiraj SDT\n-> potrebno: citljivo ime servisa (po ONID/TSID/SID)
    CORE -> SDB : upisi/azuriraj servis (triplet, ime, PID-ovi)
  end
  CORE --> SCAN : servis pronadjen i upisan u Service & Mux DB
  SCAN --> SCANL : installServiceTVName(routeId, name)
  SCAN --> SCANL : installServiceTVNumber(routeId, number)
end

SCAN --> SCANL : installStatus(ScanInstallStatus)
SCANL --> CHSC : installStatus(ScanInstallStatus)
note over CORE, CHAL : svi servisi su obradjeni

CHAL -> TSDK : zatvori section filtere + zatvori izvor (file_close/teardown)
TSDK --> CHAL : interfejs unlocked
CHAL --> CORE : izvor i demux path zatvoreni, route oslobodjen
CORE -> CORE : routeManager - oslobodi install route (routeID)

== ScanListener obavestava ChannelScanner da je instalacija (za trenutni izvor) gotova ==
CORE --> SCAN : instalacija zavrsena (interno)
SCAN --> SCANL : scanFinished(routeId)
SCANL --> CHSC : scanFinished(routeId)
note over CHSC
 ako postoji sledeci sourceUrl u listi -> nazad na appendList(true)+autoScan
 (ponavlja se petlja iz "Skeniranje kroz niz izvora");
 inace -> unregisterListener(scanListener) i javi TIS-u kraj
end note

CHSC -> SCAN : unregisterListener(scanListener)
CHSC --> TIS : onScanFinished()

== TIS preko ChannelPublisher cita rezultate iz Service & Mux DB ==

TIS -> CHPB : publishInstalledServices(inputId)

CHPB -> SVC : getServiceListCount(listIndex)
SVC -> SDB : upit nad Service & Mux DB
SDB --> SVC : broj servisa u listi
SVC --> CHPB : count

loop za svaki serviceIndex u [0, count)
  CHPB -> SVC : getServiceDescriptor(listIndex, serviceIndex)
  SVC -> SDB : upit nad Service & Mux DB
  SDB --> SVC : ServiceDescriptor podaci
  SVC --> CHPB : ServiceDescriptor\n(getName, getONID, getTSID, getServiceId, getLCN, isScrambled...)
  CHPB -> TVP : insert/update channel (TvContract.Channels)\nmapiranje: ONID/TSID/SID -> Android channel/internal_provider_data\n(keyed po ONID+TSID+serviceId tripletu)
end

CHPB --> TIS : channelCount
TIS --> App : Scan complete (onScanFinished(channelCount))

@enduml
